{"tid":2290360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌區議員王進洋阻擋TVB壟斷活動申辦權","createTime":"2020-11-18T03:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T06:39:10.000Z","uid":25240,"like":210,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c189baa20fe935461ed92a02932be9cb90d7fe27","tid":2290360,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:04:36.000Z","msg":"【東涌區議員王進洋阻擋TVB壟斷活動申辦權】<br />\n<br />\n「平日地區事務同政府交流<br />\n活動同藍色團體點有傾有笑都好<br />\n大是大非下，我一定要清晰知道自己做啲乜<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">今日開會，評分決定邊間公司可以承辦活動<br />\n我全部比零分，導致TVB輸左，我好開心<br />\n</span></span><br />\n今次，係一個政治表態<br />\n抗議過往呢一年TVB種種令人噁心嘅報導<br />\n你點搞，我都一樣比零分」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSUP8a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSUP8a6.png&h=44fb48a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nES2JKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnES2JKs.jpg&h=7e39aa28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d75acb6634f038df206545123c46878c30828f9b","tid":2290360,"uid":279333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbf75b37e637602d22b48957f0c95ba4df6a25b","tid":2290360,"uid":25240,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:05:33.000Z","msg":"我要睇tvb呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yjN6qX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyjN6qX8.jpg&h=ba8fe414&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee50efc00